        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 5. CT scan skull of Ichthyophis tricolor (University of Kerala MW 747). Views as in Fig. 2. Scale bar = 1mm. Abbreviations as in Appendix 2. Scan parameters: a molybdenum target set at 98kV and 190µA, with a reconstructed voxel size of 11µm." ;
